About

Are you a soccer enthusiast looking to take your game strategy to the next level? Look no further. At Lineup Manager, we provide you with the ultimate platform to create, customize, and analyze soccer lineups with ease. Whether you're a casual fan, a seasoned player, or even a coach, our suite of features is designed to enhance your understanding and strategy of the beautiful game.

About Us

Hello and welcome to Lineup Manager! My name is Laura Miro Rodrigo, the sole creator and developer behind this platform. As a senior at Luther College, where I also play soccer, I've combined my firsthand experience on the field with my academic background in computer science and management to bring you this specialized tool. Lineup Manager was born out of a desire to offer soccer enthusiasts—like myself—a more personalized and insightful way to create and analyze their lineups.
